---
title: Szechuan Beef & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Candied Peanuts & Jasmine Rice
description: Forget takeout: The path to sweet-spicy-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a frying pan! In this recipe, ground pork and green beans are coated in a tantalizing Szechuan-style sauce, and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping. Everything comes together over a bed of steamy rice mixed with warm, sizzly ginger—in just 30 minutes! The results? A symphony of flavors and textures so delicious, you might just lick the plate–no judgments here.
